  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.6667px;&quot;&gt;The proposed roof terrace by virtue of its design, siting and scale is considered to lead to a detrimental impact on the amenity of the neighbours in terms of overlooking, loss of privacy and noise disturbance contrary to policy LP2 (Design and amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;The proposed roof terrace and associated works, by way of its massing, design and visual prominence, would result in a visually incongruous and overly prominent addition, to the detriment of the character and appearance of the application site and the surrounding streetscene contrary to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;policies D4 (Delivering good design) and of the London Plan 2021, policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and of the Hackney Local Plan 2020 and the recommendations of the Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Extensions and Alterations 2009.&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed rear roof dormer and hip to gable roof extension, by virtue of its siting, scale, form and mass, would constitute an incongruous form of development that is not subordinate to the host building, would be uncharacteristic of the surrounding area and would fail to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of the surrounding area. As such the proposal is contrary to policies D4 (Delivering good design) and of the London Plan 2021, policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and of the Hackney Local Plan 2020 and the recommendations of the Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Extensions and Alterations 2009.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
